e before you switch sides.";i:36;s:58:"Press down with one hand to keep the floor from coming up.";i:37;s:55:"Press up the sky with the lower palm on the other hand.";i:38;s:158:"How Yoga is Helping Me Heal My Broken Ankle Its a funny thing the thoughts that run through your head when sitting on the side of a trail with a broken ankle.";i:39;s:131:"Besides wondering how I was going to get off the mountain and to a hospital I also questioned how I would ever trust my body again.";i:40;s:95:"Sit forward on your chair so that the soles of your feet can be in full contact with the floor.";i:41;s:52:"Feet and knees should be about shoulder-width apart.";i:42;s:53:"Spine is erect with the pelvis back and head aligned.";i:43;s:72:"Shoulders are relaxed and your hands are loosely resting in your thighs.";i:44;s:13:"Lets face it.";i:45;s:67:"Exercising with a broken ankle seems like a contradiction in terms.";i:46;s:191:"When exercise is tantamount to working up a sweat how are you supposed to burn calories and get summer-ready when your broken ankle is desperately crying out for you to hang out on the couch.";i:47;s:98:"Listen you dont have to resign yourself to the next six months spent lounging around on the couch.";i:48;s:25:"Yoga for Fractured Ankle.";i:49;s:107:"Delhi I had fractured my ankle in an accident and the nerve which goes from lower leg to foot was ruptured.";i:50;s:101:"After the surgery the ankle joint was fixed but recovery was all dependent on central nerve recovery.";i:51;s:64:"Doctor told me that there is 60 chance that you will be alright.";i:52;s:212:"Stay Active Mentally Staying as physically active as possible while dealing with a broken leg is very important though it is not the only aspect of your life that must be attended to during your time of recovery.";i:53;s:91:"The broken toe pose is a simple yoga move that helps relieve pain from sore feet or ankles.";i:54;s:64:"If the broken toe pose feels too difficult try these four moves.";i:55;s:30:"S